text: Kustarevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Shulganovsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 6 km from Shulganovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Kustarevka, Republic of Bashkortostan
